I'm sorry.

302
00:21:43,051 --> 00:21:45,137
Well... I was...

303
00:21:45,929 --> 00:21:47,347
-Here.
-It's okay.

304
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:49,516
Well...

305
00:21:50,267 --> 00:21:52,853
I heard that you were preparing
the Statement to the Nation.

306
00:21:53,437 --> 00:21:55,897
As the speechwriter in charge,
