to make sure you are comfortable.

311
00:22:11,079 --> 00:22:13,665
Would you like to get some sleep?
Should I prepare a bed for you?

312
00:22:14,249 --> 00:22:17,210
No, thanks. I'm good.

313
00:22:17,836 --> 00:22:20,005
All right, then.

314
00:22:20,380 --> 00:22:21,423
Thanks.

315
00:22:41,985 --> 00:22:43,403
The Blue House staff and I

316
00:22:43,862 --> 00:22:47,866
will take care of everything.

317
00:22:48,450 --> 00:22:51,912
All you have to do sir,

318
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:54,498
is just sit there.

319
00:22:55,707 --> 00:22:59,127
That way, this nation can maintain
at least a bit of constitutional order.

320
00:23:17,396 --> 00:23:19,481
It’s me. How is Si-jin?

321
00:23:22,067 --> 00:23:23,193
What did the doctor say?

322
00:23:24,611 --> 00:23:26,947
There seems to have been
some internal bleeding in her brain,

323
00:23:28,156 --> 00:23:30,117
but they were able to stop it.

324
00:23:37,082 --> 00:23:37,958
Now,

325
00:23:39,418 --> 00:23:43,004
we are waiting for Si-jin
to regain consciousness.

326
