01:03:31,182 --> 01:03:32,683
I initiate...

890
01:03:34,769 --> 01:03:36,020
DEFCON 2...

891
01:03:36,896 --> 01:03:38,022
on the Korean Peninsula.

892
01:03:41,984 --> 01:03:43,986
DEFCON 2 has been declared
for the entire military.

893
01:03:45,029 --> 01:03:47,782
DEFCON 2 has been declared
for the entire military!

894
01:03:47,865 --> 01:03:50,117
DEFCON has been declared.

895
01:03:51,869 --> 01:03:54,956
All troops get ready for combat.

896
01:03:55,790 --> 01:03:56,874
Go!

897
01:04:13,891 --> 01:04:14,725
What did you say?

898
01:04:19,689 --> 01:04:20,648
Mr. President.

899
01:04:21,941 --> 01:04:25,695
North Korea has issued
Level 2 Combat Readiness.

900
01:04:32,118 --> 01:04:33,119
I know.

901
01:04:34,495 --> 01:04:37,081
Get them ready now.

902
01:04:38,583 --> 01:04:39,417
Okay.

903
01:04:43,004 --> 01:04:44,338
Call Washington

904
01:04:44,422 --> 01:04:46,507
and upgrade to DEFCON 1.

905
01:04:48,050 --> 01:04:49,594
Bloody Nose.

906
01:04:50,386 --> 01:04:52,722
It's time for that strategy.

907
01:05:22,668 --> 01:05:23,502
This is the Blue House.

908
01:05:29,258 --> 01:05:31,093
Mr. President has to answer.

909
01:05:51,364 --> 01:05:53,032
This is Park Mu-jin,

910
01:05:55,076 --> 01:05:56,243
the acting president.

911
01:06:02,625 --> 01:06:07,296
Did you say you have the coordinates
to the current location of our submarine?

912
01:06:12,802 --> 01:06:15,012
CALL OFF LEVEL 2 COMBAT READINESS

