01:06:22,311 --> 01:06:24,105
Then I'll send you
the submarine's coordinates.

916
01:06:24,188 --> 01:06:27,316
The South breached
the ceasefire agreement first.

917
01:06:28,109 --> 01:06:30,403
You called in Japan's
Maritime Self-defense Force

918
01:06:30,486 --> 01:06:33,239
and went into combat readiness
with the US.

919
01:06:33,823 --> 01:06:37,159
It was the South, not us.

920
01:06:39,036 --> 01:06:42,164
Why would we lift combat readiness first?

921
01:06:43,791 --> 01:06:45,459
Is it because of the US?

922
01:06:46,627 --> 01:06:50,131
Because they have wartime authority,
not the South?

923
01:06:56,679 --> 01:06:59,015
NO NEGOTIATIONS WITHOUT AN ANSWER

924
01:07:00,266 --> 01:07:01,267
It's because...

925
01:07:03,686 --> 01:07:04,854
we aren't the US.

926
01:07:10,026 --> 01:07:12,278
The US doesn't want peace
on the Korean Peninsula

927
01:07:13,154 --> 01:07:14,321
as much as we do.

928
01:07:18,701 --> 01:07:20,828
The crew of the submarine are still alive,

929
01:07:21,287 --> 01:07:23,956
but the window of opportunity
may close if you wait any longer.

930
01:07:25,624 --> 01:07:29,420
Isn't it the nation's duty
to save its people's lives?

931
01:07:31,213 --> 01:07:32,214
Today,

932
01:07:33,883 --> 01:07:35,551
we failed to do so.

933
01:07:35,801 --> 01:07:38,137
However, you still have a chance.

934
01:08:12,922 --> 01:08:14,215
Look!

935
01:08:15,508 --> 01:08:18,636
North Korean combat planes are moving!

936
01:08:23,933 --> 01:08:25,935
What did I tell you?

937
01:08:26,018 --> 01:08:28,562
They used this conversation
to take advantage of us!

938
01:08:29,563 --> 01:08:33,067
We gave North Korea time to attack us!

939
01:08:33,651 --> 01:08:35,361
No, we didn't.

940
01:08:35,444 --> 01:08:38,030
The combat planes are turning around.

941
01:08:39,073 --> 01:08:41,492
The fighter jets heading toward the MDL

942
01:08:41,575 --> 01:08:43,369
