943
01:08:50,626 --> 01:08:52,962
Okay, good. The North

944
01:08:53,462 --> 01:08:56,090
has lifted its combat readiness.

945
01:09:01,053 --> 01:09:03,139
President Park... Please.

946
01:09:03,305 --> 01:09:04,348
Right, of course.

947
01:09:13,440 --> 01:09:16,193
These are the coordinates
to where the submarine drifted.

948
01:09:28,497 --> 01:09:29,540
Sir.

949
01:09:30,958 --> 01:09:33,961
Please lower our state to DEFCON 4.

