01:09:46,223 --> 01:09:47,808
We are now at DEFCON 4.

951
01:09:48,559 --> 01:09:50,686
It's time to keep your promise.

952
01:09:56,150 --> 01:10:00,070
Will you remove the Sawagiri fleet
from Korean waters?

953
01:10:44,740 --> 01:10:46,700
It's just a cramp.

954
01:10:55,584 --> 01:10:58,921
SINUIJU

955
01:10:59,004 --> 01:11:03,217
PEACE AND PROSPERITY

956
01:11:12,476 --> 01:11:14,228
Is it being sent to NDFC?

957
01:11:14,812 --> 01:11:18,148
A photo or video of the explosion
would help,

958
01:11:18,232 --> 01:11:20,693
but I doubt there’s any.
