959
01:11:20,776 --> 01:11:23,279
They could find a lead
in one of these devices.

960
01:11:24,154 --> 01:11:27,032
I don't know how much
forensics can recover, but still.

961
01:11:33,247 --> 01:11:36,000
Do we have consent
from all the victims' families?

962
01:11:37,084 --> 01:11:40,129
There are some from missing persons
who haven't been confirmed dead or alive.

963
01:11:54,351 --> 01:11:57,438
I'll wrap up things here
and send the evidence to NDFC.

